data.description: Come home to this beautiful 4 bedroom 3 bath home in the sought after subdivision of Vineland Park.  Walking in you'll immediately notice the high ceilings and the fresh new paint. The lucky new owners will enjoy the open kitchen/living room concept this home has to offer; it comes completed with granite, stainless steel appliances, an island and a pantry. You'll find the grand bedroom on the second floor along with two other rooms. The grand bedroom includes a spacious bathroom and a walk in closet. The features continue as the 4th bedroom and an additional living room can be found in the basement. Don't miss the opportunity to have a like new home that has so much to offer!! Did I mention the privacy fence, a shed and an above ground pool for summer fun?! Call me or your agent today for an appointment!
